{"tid":383904,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"先安內而後攘外，占自身","createTime":"2017-09-02T00:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T12:35:29.000Z","uid":129128,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f491d45c7810a9e65332198d2e60f250f251691","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:14:48.000Z","msg":"自身卦係一種好大範圍嘅事，但會離唔開你日常生活嘅事，都可以係一種修心嘅卦，從而改善運氣<br />\n只占一事，有咩事都可以占，但唔占賭博，同埋會打比你講返比你知，因為比較詳細啲，問問題一定要詳細<br />\n留低你中文全名，出生日期，男定女，問咩事，盡量全部都占<br />\n可以占孕婦，官司，失物/人，家居風水，，買樓租樓，生意，出門遠行，自身卦，奇難集症等等等等<br />\n未夠18歲唔占<br />\nwhatsapp 59891042"},{"pid":"e86c1ae7fefe38aa4413ec1fc64cef69f921226f","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:22:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"704d0ee89fba9d743a10544a20cd3a0a9bdaf0c3","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:26:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4f72f6e2ca2bec54faab8c14e9db0642d06ddee","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:28:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4e5cf7480c0696d1f39258d68f109cb51d5c579","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:35:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dd9946def58013fb9d39f4b90b2fc738d533e4b","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:37:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42f64f3a0bfdc12fffcee015db5890a6cbccacf4","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:40:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dff320002f92f9db8bba322c7886755b5f5a0423","tid":383904,"uid":106998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:45:55.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"4ee6746b4807ffe8476b123bb08f385ec923cc65","tid":383904,"uid":129128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T00:47:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc83e60d6dbefa41fdd9198b3d28fb7dbb902d4","tid":